							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Feign death is part of the self invisibility line. It's not a big loss, although it safed my ass a few times when eg raids went the wrong way. But do the "cancel all maintained spells when fd" bug i am happy to have an invisibility that does not destroy all my maintains when it breaks. Although they fix that when they take away the fd from us  <img src="images/smiles/icon_confused.gif" alt="Confused" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Combat changes for brigands will be nice, there are a few drawbacks (fd, bows vs thrown, group invis) but most stuff will be great as far as i can see.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
